    <title>准备食用RAC(ReactiveCocoa)的顾虑</title>
    <link href="https://madordie.github.io/2016/07/12/reactivecocoa-ready-to-use/"/>
    <id>https://madordie.github.io/2016/07/12/reactivecocoa-ready-to-use/</id>
